      <div class="msgContentFrame">I have made a ton of macros to make the game easier, I figured I would share one that would probably help alot of people <br /> <br /><b>Phantom Dart</b> <br />/ac &quot;Phantom Dart&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br />/wait 2 <br />/ac &quot;Phantom Dart&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br />/wait 2 <br />/ac &quot;Phantom Dart&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br />/wait 2 <br /> <br />You can do it up to 5 times, but it locks you out so you cant emergency heal, I found 3 to be a good balance. It takes alot of the pain out of spamming your dart <br /> <br /><b>Sacrifice</b> <br />/aoe <br />/ac &quot;Sacrifice&quot; &lt;me&gt; <br />/wait 5 <br />/aoe <br /> <br />Allows you to AOE your cure <br /> <br />And then just do all your other spells  <br /><b>Poison</b> <br />/ac &quot;Poison&quot; &lt;t&gt; <br /> <br /> <br />Doing it this way lets you avoid the aoe click on the screen, of course you could have a second aoe macro to hit first to let you turn it on then use all your spells as aoe's <br />etc etc.. <br />I have also made class change jobs to make it much faster changing from my thaum to my miner. <br /> <br /> <br />Anyone else have helpful macros they wanna share?</div>
