      <div class="msgContentFrame">For buffs put in a /p Gather together macro to let them know it's an AOE buff. <br /> <br />Make a macro for JUST /aoe. <br /> <br />Any other macro you want to be AOE, make sure you use /AOE on, then /AOE off. Otherwise it may not work as affected. <br /> <br />/p HP: &lt;hp&gt; &lt;hpp&gt; MP: &lt;mp&gt; &lt;mpp&gt; Alerts your party of how much HP and MP you have, in case you're low on HP and will die from aggro or not enough MP to cast. <br /> <br />/br  <br />/p Starting battle regimen with Banish / PHantom Dart / whatever <br />/ac &quot;Phantom Dart&quot; &lt;t&gt; Then press g to initiate the regimen.</div>
      <div class="msgFtFrame">
