      <div class="msgContentFrame">eh, for making spells be aoes, this has been really helpful for me. <br /> <br />/aoe on <br />/ac &quot;Sacrifice&quot; &lt;me&gt; <br />/aoe off <br /> <br />the &lt;me&gt; makes it so you cast it on ppl around you who are infront of you (not behind).  <br />you can change it to &lt;t&gt; to be casting the aoe around your target <br />&lt;p1&gt; or &lt;p2&gt; and so on to be cast on a specific party member. <br /> <br />I have my Sacrifice on 4 (for single target casting) <br />this macro on ctrl 4 (for aoe only) and then be able to effectively cast spells without worrying if i'm in aoe or single target mode. <br /> <br />I use this macro for Cure and Stoneskin and any other buff spells, you use this for all of them too, like Dia, Scourge and such.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1817536.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
